{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013tGLkPxLQw8hr78sRfH37V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem! The `elasticsearch.yml` ConfigMap is missing the `cluster.initial_master_nodes` setting. This is an Elasticsearch 7.x cluster and for a brand new cluster, you need `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to bootstrap the cluster. Without it, no master can be elected.\n\nThe `cluster.initial_master_nodes` setting is a bootstrap-only setting that:\n1. Must be set on initial startup to allow a quorum of master nodes to form\n2. Must be **removed** after the cluster forms (as stated in the goal)\nThe current configuration has the basic settings like cluster name, node roles, and discovery seed hosts, but it's missing that critical bootstrap parameter. The solution is to add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` listing the three nodes to the ConfigMap, then remove it once the cluster successfully elects a master. config and verify the cluster remains stable through the rolling restart. But I need to be careful here—the constraint is to use existing resources without recreating the cluster, so I can't just delete pods recklessly. The real issue is that the three pods are stuck because `cluster.initial_master_nodes` is missing from the ConfigMap, preventing them from forming a quorum. My approach is to add this setting to the ConfigMap, then do a controlled rolling restart by deleting pods one at a time so the StatefulSet controller brings them back up with the new configuration, and finally wait for the cluster to reach a healthy state.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":513,"cache_read_input_tokens":35455,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":513},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"382c2cfa-d730-404f-a4dd-d5172a27f258","uuid":"a8bc25c7-08f1-4ffc-9d4b-05634854d99e","request_id":"req_011CcMSBNLd1Ee19Sc6Ezedg"}
