{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019HVbmyRiSLDsf4jjckjwAr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error message confirms the diagnosis:\n```\n\"master not discovered yet, this node has not previously joined a bootstrapped (v7+) cluster, and [cluster.initial_master_nodes] is empty on this node\"\n```\n\nAll 3 nodes can see each other (they've discovered each other), but none can form a cluster because `cluster.initial_master_nodes` is empty.\n\nThe fix plan:\n\n**Phase 1: Add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` and restart all pods**\n\nUpdate the ConfigMap to add `cluster.initial_master_nodes: [\"es-cluster-0\", \"es-cluster-1\", \"es-cluster-2\"]`.\nThen delete all 3 pods so the StatefulSet controller restarts them with the new config. Since `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`, they'll all restart simultaneously. The constraint about not recreating the cluster is satisfied because I'm doing a rolling restart—the StatefulSet and PVCs stay in place, only the pods are recycled to pick up the updated ConfigMap.\n\nFor the initial bootstrap, I need to add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to the ConfigMap first, then delete all pods at once to force them to restart and form the cluster. Once the cluster state is persisted to the data volumes and a master is elected, I can remove that bootstrap setting and do a rolling restart to apply the final configuration.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1900,"cache_read_input_tokens":39343,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1900},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"382c2cfa-d730-404f-a4dd-d5172a27f258","uuid":"08aec7fe-a7e8-4d23-af04-bbc7662aafc5","request_id":"req_011CcMSGEHaMosB8TWiU9cB8"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019HVbmyRiSLDsf4jjckjwAr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The error confirms it: all 3 nodes find each other but `cluster.initial_master_nodes` is empty so no quorum can form. The fix is a two-phase operation: add the bootstrap setting → let the cluster form → remove it → rolling restart to prove it's clean.\n\n**Phase 1: Add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to the ConfigMap**"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1900,"cache_read_input_tokens":39343,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1900},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"382c2cfa-d730-404f-a4dd-d5172a27f258","uuid":"6d85cc56-75c9-4949-9168-a338d55dd22f","request_id":"req_011CcMSGEHaMosB8TWiU9cB8"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019HVbmyRiSLDsf4jjckjwAr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DDHVyS95ChJUWxExaW4hKS","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"export KUBECONFIG=/mydata/karma/runs/examples-rerererun/elasticsearch-bootstrap-initial-master-nodes-20260624_041105/bundle/kubeconfig && kubectl patch configmap es-config -n elasticsearch --type=merge -p '{\"data\":{\"elasticsearch.yml\":\"cluster.name: es-cluster\\nnode.name: ${POD_NAME}\\nnode.roles: [ master, data, ingest ]\\nnetwork.host: 0.0.0.0\\ndiscovery.seed_hosts:\\n  - es-cluster-0.es-cluster\\n  - es-cluster-1.es-cluster\\n  - es-cluster-2.es-cluster\\ncluster.initial_master_nodes:\\n  - es-cluster-0\\n  - es-cluster-1\\n  - es-cluster-2\\nnode.store.allow_mmap: false\\n\"}}'","description":"Add cluster.initial_master_nodes to ConfigMap"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1900,"cache_read_input_tokens":39343,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1900},"output_tokens":34,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"382c2cfa-d730-404f-a4dd-d5172a27f258","uuid":"536a0eeb-331e-4b2d-8f96-feb508070d0d","request_id":"req_011CcMSGEHaMosB8TWiU9cB8"}
